# Testing Standards

- Use Vitest for tests.
- Keep reusable test utilities in `__tests__/utils/`.
- Use factories in `__tests__/factories/` for test data.
- Prefer behavior-focused assertions over implementation details.
- For bug fixes, add or update tests that fail before the fix and pass after it.
